Name: Old Student ID
AttributesDescription: An old student ID from Startorch Academy, said to have been yours once.
BgDescription:
The student ID Chisa unintentionally took amid the Void Storm.
The ID is eroded, but you can still make out your face in the picture.
Twenty-odd years ago, you once roamed the halls of Startorch Academy.
ObtainedShowDescription: An old student ID from Startorch Academy, said to have been yours once. Its surface marked by years of erosion.
